    "The low density of the air in the lungs makes them appear black on the radiograph.",
    "Given the increasing prevalence and the complexity of diagnosing kidney stones, there is an urgent need for innovative diagnostic techniques.",
    "Traditional imaging techniques may produce low-quality images, making interpreting results easier.",
